    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Culture and style of Native North Americans who historically occupied the areas in Idaho, Montana, and Washington when Europeans arrived, particularly the area around what is now called Lake Pend Oreille. Today, the Kalispel are recognized as the "Kalispel Indian Community" in Washington and are members of the Confederated Salish &amp; Kootenai Tribes in Montana.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000050812/Kalispel Tribe of Indians (2009-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000106006/NCSL, Federal and State Recognized Tribes (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cultuur en de stijl van de inheemse mensen die gebieden in Idaho, Montana en Washington bewoonden toen de Europeanen arriveerden, met name het gebied rond wat nu heet 'Lake Pend Oreille'.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052384/Billard, De indianen (1978)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>在歐洲人抵達美洲時，歷史上分佈於現今愛達荷州、蒙大拿州與華盛頓州，特別是愛達荷州境內龐德湖／旁德瑞湖（Lake Pend Oreille）周遭地區之北美原住民所屬文化與風格。今日，卡力司佩在華盛頓州認可為｢卡力司佩印地安人社區｣（Kalispel Indian Community），在蒙大拿州並成為｢薩利什與庫特內同盟部族｣（Confederated Salish &amp; Kootenai Tribes）成員之一。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
